  <name>SysManage Agent</name>
  <summary>System management and monitoring agent</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      SysManage Agent is a lightweight system monitoring and management agent
      that collects system information and sends it to a SysManage server for
      centralized monitoring and management.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Real-time system monitoring (CPU, memory, disk, network)</li>
      <li>Hardware inventory collection</li>
      <li>Software package tracking</li>
      <li>User and access management monitoring</li>
      <li>Secure WebSocket communication with SysManage server</li>
      <li>Cross-platform support (Linux, BSD, Windows, macOS)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Note: This Flatpak provides read-only monitoring capabilities due to
      sandbox restrictions. For full management features (package installation,
      firewall management, etc.), use the native packages (DEB/RPM).
    </p>
  </description>

